text: Shooting at the 2005 Southeast Asian Games was split into two venues: *Trap and Skeet in PNSA Clay Target Range, Muntinlupa City, Metro Manila, Philippines. *Air Pistol, Rifle, Practical in the PSC-PNSA Shooting Range BNS in Fort Bonifacio, Taguig City, Metro Manila, Philippines. ==Medal winners== {| class="wikitable" |- !
